<Layout title="Privacy Policy — Walensis">
  <h1>Walensis Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="muted">Last updated: April 11, 2026</p>

  <p>
    Walensis is the publisher of Deal Lens and operates walensis.com. This
    page explains how we handle data at the company level. Each Walensis
    product has its own product-specific privacy policy linked below.
  </p>

  <h2>This website</h2>
  <p>
    walensis.com is a static marketing site. It does not set analytics or
    advertising cookies, does not use tracking pixels, and does not collect
    personal information from visitors. Your web browser and our hosting
    provider (Cloudflare) may record standard request logs for security and
    reliability purposes; we do not use those logs for profiling or
    advertising.
  </p>

  <h2>Product privacy policies</h2>
  <p>
    Data handling for Walensis products is covered by product-specific
    policies:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <a href="/deal-lens/privacy">Deal Lens Privacy Policy</a> — covers the
      Deal Lens Chrome extension, account data, and listing analysis.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    For privacy questions, email
    <a href="mailto:privacy@walensis.com">privacy@walensis.com</a>.
  </p>
</Layout>
